{"tid":1412134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［罷買文宣］知慳識儉，咪做大嘥鬼","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:31:11.000Z","uid":53003,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bbaff4da5a1a089f62b751f7a7b87af5ecb9b68a","tid":1412134,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:34:10.000Z","msg":"之前有人提議罷買，有人覺得唔work。但大家需知道資本主義的運作模式，就係鼓勵人消費，所以只要大家一齊減低消費，必然對香港做成打擊。<br />\n<br />\n文宣方面，建議大家可以用節儉為題，仲可以用埋大嘥鬼，鼓勵大家減低消費，我相信咁樣可以鼓勵一班溫和的人加入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/9a/Big_waster.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20151012144548\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F9a%2FBig_waster.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20151012144548&h=8c85c644&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc25a7ccb1db0b85815ab87fdd1173eb251093ab","tid":1412134,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a98b14fe6c1c5c919bcee4d69b83fb4b8cf247","tid":1412134,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"connect埋環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d34c6eec89b4875b42cd330a59f2d79878ad48","tid":1412134,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15a98b14fe6c1c5c919bcee4d69b83fb4b8cf247","tid":1412134,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"connect埋環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb44962e10cf0bc160584654c4293464b1a79432","tid":1412134,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:10